'''Princess''' was [[Lisa Simpson|Lisa]]'s [[pony]] in "[[Lisa's Pony]]". Homer buys her for Lisa, hoping to regain her love again after he disappoints her one time too many. The pony is expensive to own, so Homer gets a second job at the [[Kwik-E-Mart]] along with his job at the [[Springfield Nuclear Power Plant]] causing him to become overly stressed. Lisa realizes that Homer has made a large sacrifice for the pony, so she gives up Princess.
